claim.claim-text:
A gas turbine system (10), comprising:
a rotor wheel (32);
a plurality of impeller vanes (40) radially disposed on the rotor wheel (32);
a plurality of fluid passages (36) defined by adjacent impeller vanes (40) such that the plurality of fluid passages (36) are radially disposed across the rotor wheel (32) ; and
one or more shape memory alloy valves (44) disposed within one or more of the plurality of fluid passages (36), the one or more shape memory alloy valves (44) configured to change shape to control a flow of fluid (46) through the fluid passages (36).

A gas turbine system (10), comprising:
a rotor (24) comprising a plurality of rotor wheels (32);
a plurality of impeller vanes (40) radially disposed on each of the rotor wheels (32);
a plurality of fluid passages (36) defined by adjacent impeller vanes (40) such that the plurality of fluid passages (36) are radially disposed across the rotor wheels (32); and
one or more shape memory alloy valves (44) disposed within one or more of the plurality of fluid passages (36), the one or more shape memory alloy valves (44) configured to change shape to control a flow of fluid (46) through the fluid passages (36).
